original: Lindgren, Sthlm, Karl-Evert 27. — Genomg. Katrineholmis tekn. sk. Plats-red. f. Ostgöta Correspond. i Mjölby sed. 26. Led. av stadsfullm. 37-40, v. ordf. där 38-40, led. av drätselkamm. 34-40, av fastigh :ndn o. i styr. f. stadsbibi. i Mjölby 36-40, led. av styr. f. östergötl. länsförb. av allm. valm:-förb. o. dess arb :utsk. 34-40, ordf. i Mjölby mod. valm:fören. 34-40, löjtn. i armén 33.
translated: Lindgren, Stockholm, Karl-Evert 27. - Completed technical school in Katrineholm. Editor for Ostgöta Correspondenten in Mjölby since 1926. Member of the city council from 1937 to 1940, vice chairman from 1938 to 1940. Member of the finance committee from 1934 to 1940, member of the real estate committee and on the board of the city library in Mjölby from 1936 to 1940. Member of the board for the East Gothland County Association of General Elections and its working committee from 1934 to 1940. Chairman of the Mjölby Modern Election Society from 1934 to 1940. Lieutenant in the army since 1933.
